overview: Join the Motorbikin team as they tackle a no holds barred 3000  kilometre run north from Brisbane to Darwin via Lawn Hill, Edith Falls and all the good stuff in between! We revisit our Orange Vtwin roots and check out BMWs Ultimate Enduro machine while the Dirty Old DR just keeps on thumping!  Theres plenty more to see as we thrash Suzukis new Vstrom 1000 and another little segment we might just call "The Ramp"
title: Motorbikin' 17: Hells Gate
